!TITLE
SYMBOLIC NUMBERS AND COLORS IN APOCALYTPIC WRITINGS
!WORDS
SYMBOLIC NUMBERS IN APOCALYPTIC WRITINGS
3 – meaning a few, limited number or limited time
4. - universality (as in the four corner of the earth)
7 – perfection or completeness
10 – completion of a cycle or perfect order
12 – fullness or completeness
1000 - -a number too big to count
42 mos. (or 3 ½ years) which is half of 7, a limited
     time of harassment


COLORS IN APOCALYPTIC WRITINGS
White – victory
Red – violence or bloodshed
Scarlet – royalty and bloodshed
Purple – royalty
Pale green – death
White & red – mark out the two side of a great battle
       Between good and evil  (Revelation)
