!TITLE
A BOY AND HIS DOG
!WORDS
By Evie Zimmerman     Trendingly  4/5/23

When a little 4-year-old boy went missing, his family were frantic. 
It would be authorities who finally tracked him down in the forest. 
Other than a lost shoe, the little boy was safe, thanks in part to 
the family dog (a Labrador Retriever) who had refused to leave his 
side throughout the ordeal.
