is an absurdity and there is absolutely no need for it. What the 
world needs is not "a little bit of love," but major surgery. If you 
think you are helping lost people with your sympathy and 
understanding, you are a traitor to Jesus Christ. You must have a 
right-standing relationship with Him yourself, and pour your life out 
in helping others in His way— not in a human way that ignores God. ”

“God does not give us overcoming life; He gives us life as we 
overcome.”

