fear, and doubt. He is always there to encourage our hearts and help 
us understand that He’s sufficient for all our needs. When I accepted 
this as an absolute truth in my life, I found that my worrying 
stopped.” 

“The circumstances and events that we see as setbacks are oftentimes 
the very things that launch us into periods of intense spiritual 
growth.”
