----------------------------------------------------
A West Virginia man goes to his father and says, "Daddy, I'm going to 
divorce my wife."  The father says, "That's terrible, son.  You just 
married her yesterday.  What's the problem?"? The son says, "She's a 
virgin."  The father replies, "Oh, Lord!  I guess I don't blame you, 
son.  If she's not good enough for her family, she's certainly not 
good enough for ours."

