!TITLE
6 MYTHS WE TELL ABOUT GEORGE WASHINGTON
!WORDS
1. The Cherry Tree story
     It never happpened.

2. That he was the first president to live in the White House. 
     It wasn't built until 1800, the year after his death.

3. That he had wooden dentures. 
