!TITLE
LIVING TIDAL - SHEENA JEFFERS
!WORDS
On a frigid November night at high tide, a young woman unties the 
dock lines and watches the land recede as the sailboat she's standing 
on floats out to sea. She has a jacket, a scarf, and a deep need to 
reinvent herself. Living Tidal is part adventure, part love story: a 
coming-of-age memoir that captures the hearts and minds of readers 
with each page. Journalist Sheena Jeffers addresses the curiosity, 
self-doubt, and the desire we all have to deeply experience the world 
as we embark on the lifelong journey to know ourselves.

