!TITLE
CHILDREN KILLED IN GAZA FIGHTING
!WORDS
UVA Professor Ogunnaike thought the whole episode was due to 
political polarization. In fact, he said, everyone should oppose the 
killing of civilians.

“More children have been killed in Gaza in the last few months than 
in all the wars of the last four years combined. Whatever your 
politics, this is simply unacceptable. We should not and must not 
continue business as usual. This calls for protest. “   5/10/24
