FAMILY, WAS KILLED BY AN ASSASSIN'S BULLET WHILE A CONVICTED CRIMINA 
AND RAPIST HAS A MINOR EAR INJURY AND WALKS OFF.  WHERE WAS GOD WHEN 
NEEDLY, HURTING PEOPLE NEEDED A MIRALCE? THE CRIMINAL GOT ONE.
